        {
          "id": "4",
          "text": "A library system has two tables; one for borrowers and one for books. Extracts from these tables are shown. Borrower_ID Borrower_name Contact_telephone Contact_emai5404 Susan Stranks 01632 960321 rockit@cambridgeinternational.org 9867 Fei Hong Zhao 07700 900222 tawara@cambridgeinternational.org Borrowers table Book_ID ISBN Name_of_book Author_of_book Date_published Borrower_ID Date_due_back",
