    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "parts": [
        {
          "id": "5c",
          "text": "The data type for Contact_telephone has been set as text. Explain why this field has been set to text rather than integer. ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... .............................................................................................................................................",
          "marks": 2,
          "level": 1,
          "parentId": "5"
        },
        {
          "id": "5d",
          "text": "At the end of each day the tables are searched to issue reminders to borrowers about books that are overdue. Describe the automatic processing involved in searching and issuing of reminders for overdue books. ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... .............................................................................................................................................",
          "marks": 6,
          "level": 1,
          "parentId": "5"
        },
        {
          "id": "5a",
          "text": "Keeping data secure is very important in any computer system. Many organisations use encryption when sending data. Describe the term encryption. ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... .............................................................................................................................................",
          "marks": 4,
          "level": 1,
          "parentId": "5"
        },
        {
          "id": "5b",
          "text": "Keeping data secure is very important in any computer system. Many organisations use encryption when sending data. Another way of protecting data in a computer system is to use passwords. Identify methods to prevent hackers from gaining knowledge of someone’s password. ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... ................................................................................................................................................... .............................................................................................................................................",
          "marks": 4,
